{"tid":122880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網上辱罵主審法官做「狗官」 司法機構轉介律政司跟進","createTime":"2017-02-16T11:34:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-16T12:50:00.000Z","uid":41404,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"09aa39756673e0f0fe66e55deaf2301463a77207","tid":122880,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T11:34:33.000Z","msg":"7警案日前的裁決結果，惹來一些聲稱「撐警」人士不滿，發表辱罵法官的言論，例如導演高志森在facebook涉嫌辱罵法官為「狗官」，「黃絲法官偏幫亂港反港份子」，稱「本土港獨暴徒縱火、打警察、破壞公物，狗官就輕判、甚至判無罪，實在偏頗至極」。今日司法機構回應傳媒查詢，表示就近日「有人在社交媒體發表對個別法官的評論」，「司法機構對事件高度關注，已將事件轉介律政司跟進」。<br />\n<br />\n藍絲facebook專頁「9up新聞」曾指名道姓辱罵主審的外籍法官杜大衞做「狗官」，又語帶恐嚇稱「去死啦你」，相關侮辱法官言論獲大批「藍絲」留言力撐，有人形容「黑暗司法」並指裁決「無天理」。昨晚律政司回應傳媒查詢時，稱根據《基本法》第85條，香港特區法院獨立進行審判，不受任何干涉，強調司法獨立是法治的其中最重要一環，而香港的司法獨立情況亦獲得國際社會的認同。<br />\n大律師公會新任主席林定國早前曾於電台節目表示，對社會漸多針對法官的無理謾罵和威脅性言論感到擔憂和憤怒，認為無理批評不斷出現，日久定必削弱大眾對司法制度的尊重和信心，而大家縱有言論自由評論法官判決，但評論應基於充份了解有關案件的證據和法官的判案理由後才提出，用字和態度也應保持克制，以表示基本禮貌和尊重。"},{"pid":"ac1047027f0bdbf923245d9ae2a649a181611d93","tid":122880,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T11:35:47.000Z","msg":"屌咁都唔告就真係司法黑暗"},{"pid":"ac6e9b4caecd10b1739876559a129d4bf5375678","tid":122880,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T11:41:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌咁都唔告就真係司法黑暗</blockquote><br />\n律政司點會告藍屍呀"},{"pid":"7654ff7a4af9c3d80c14f0fd2245bfc24b59b30f","tid":122880,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T11:42:11.000Z","msg":"律政司睬你都on9"},{"pid":"05f647bfee6331ede51feac376450a0a459b1724","tid":122880,"uid":23160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T11:54:51.000Z","msg":"因間又證據不足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed7d1fd16e74ae301acbaeee34792e0addb7c90e","tid":122880,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T11:56:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"705b108b47edf9a5f639255679ed6f01dd1e68af","tid":122880,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T12:00:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌咁都唔告就真係司法黑暗</blockquote><br />\n律政司點會告藍屍呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n政府換屆前，好難講架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffd6a9b7e8f79d2c2d5a2fe331d999050d6e1986","tid":122880,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T12:01:45.000Z","msg":"唔記得邊個講過網上既野唔可以盡信呢"},{"pid":"95b0ac46201cc8411e4f2794a4670969e7bfc39b","tid":122880,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T12:31:34.000Z","msg":"唔通講兩句就告咩，除非低智森唔識收口。"},{"pid":"516ca07f36f6f7a57c940d596b99a80a63ad8d0e","tid":122880,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T12:34:16.000Z","msg":"告不誠實使用電腦罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3969eb0c4f0a2255d75b8f7575b4b53c4dc2142","tid":122880,"uid":6113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T12:35:40.000Z","msg":"唔係狗官，佢講九姑娘者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c34f59d550f08767ac78d9e010009fd6f4e3355","tid":122880,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T12:36:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>告不誠實使用電腦罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最後應該不了了之 蛇鼠一窩"},{"pid":"8e75c1064da344e9645a752ec63b71dcea479e2a","tid":122880,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T12:37:05.000Z","msg":"高生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7551a2e7089ae17b16ba4e8f47d1c8ef89c17008","tid":122880,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"